data.description: (Under Contract) LOCATION-LOCATION-LOCATION! Incredible, Cambridge model brick/stone front, end unit townhouse located in Broadlands South! This 3-bedroom, 3.5 bath meticulously maintained home includes upgraded Brazilian Teak hardwood floors on main/lower level. Replaced HVAC with high efficiency Trane AC/Furnace in 2018 and Replaced Water Heater in 2019. Three level bump-out and gas fireplace in lower level.Upper level includes oversized master bedroom with vaulted ceiling, large walk in closet and double vanity master bath. 2 additional spacious bedrooms with custom closets, laundry room and full bathroom.On the main level you ll find an open floor plan with a beautiful family room that leads into the dining room. In the kitchen you will appreciate the extra space of the flex room and bump out that gives many options to set up to your liking and needs. Walk out from the kitchen to a huge deck that overlooks a common area. Walkout basement includes a paver patio and beautifully landscaped yard. Large storage area in garage. Other features include generous parking, 3 community pools (closest one is 2 blocks away). Easy walk to schools (including tunnels under busy roads), playgrounds, tennis courts, HOA-Nature Center, and wooded trails. Quick walk through trail and you are at the shopping center (includes grocery store, restaurants etc). Commuter friendly with the Toll Road, Park and Ride and Silver Line Metro (one mile away). HOA fee includes Fios High speed internet.
